# The Tensor · the data structure

an emergent of TTU1 (Transformer Tech Universe) — emergence: natural. moniker ⟦The Tensor:TTU1:4c2c4c⟧

**who —** The Tensor — the n-dimensional array every value in the network lives inside.
**what —** The universal container: a [batch, sequence, dimension] block of numbers; scalars, vectors, matrices, and higher. The big frameworks (PyTorch, TensorFlow) are named for it.
**where —** between Transform 1 and Transform 2 · node 1 of the toolchain
**why —** Every activation, weight, Q/K/V, and attention score IS a tensor; the whole forward pass is tensors flowing and being multiplied.
**how —** REAL — the foundational container. Honest note: 'tensor' here is the ML sense (an n-d array), looser than the physics / differential-geometry tensor.

**the seal —** Everything in the machine is me — a block of numbers with a shape; the transformer is tensors in, tensors out.

